Segun Oni, the Social Democratic Party (SDP) governorship candidate in Ekiti, has alleged that Kayode Fayemi, the state governor, prevented the party’s presidential candidate, Adewole Adebayo, from entering the state. Mr Oni spoke while addressing the crowd of supporters at the Ekiti Parapo Pavilion in Ado Ekiti on Thursday. “They are scared, they said Segun Oni said he isn’t contesting anymore…they said I have met with Asiwaju and that I’m no longer interested,” <img data-attachment-id="537474" data-permalink="https://www.premiumtimesng.com/regional/ssouth-west/537431-ekiti-2022-sdp-presidential-candidate-prevented-from-entering-ekiti-segun-oni.html/attachment/whatsapp-image-2022-06-16-at-6-26-30-pm" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/media.premiumtimesng.com/wp-content/files/2022/06/WhatsApp-Image-2022-06-16-at-6.26.30-PM.jpeg?fit=1280%2C960&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="1280,960" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="SDP supporters in Ado-Ekiti" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;SDP supporters in Ado-Ekiti&lt;/p&gt;
